          Fair warnings first, if you're easily offended or brimming with religious zeal then go ahead and skip this post. Religion is for those individuals too weak or otherwise unwilling/incapable of accepting life for face value. It's a support group for those who live in fear of death. It's an excuse for everything. It's a hypocrisy. It's whatever the fuck you want it to be to support your own personal ends. Do you really need that GOD to tell you what's wrong or right? How to live your life? To tell you to be good or else you'll rot in hell? I could go on and on and on about why I'm right and you're wrong, and I'm sure you could too. Rest assured neither of us are going to back down because of your infallible fear of uncertainty and my not-giving-a-fuck.<br /><br />Though, if this is the start of a long debate about religion then I'll see you in a few months e3r<br /><br />
